<b>Target Sleep Hours:</b><br/>
How many hours you want to sleep each night. Most adults need 7-9 hours.<br/><br/>

<b>Wake Time:</b><br/>
When you want to wake up each day. The app calculates your bedtime based on this.<br/><br/>

<b>Target Sleep Efficiency:</b><br/>
Percentage of time in bed actually sleeping. 85% is excellent - it means out of 8 hours in bed, you sleep 6.8 hours.<br/><br/>

<b>How it works:</b><br/>
- Set wake time: 7:00 AM<br/>
- Set sleep hours: 8 hours<br/>
- App shows bedtime: 11:00 PM<br/>
- Work time remaining until 11:00 PM
